original_title: Animal Rescue: Vol. 2: Best Cat Rescues
overview: Cats might have nine lives, but that doesn't keep them out of the harrowing life-or-death rescue situations captured in this thrilling volume of highlights from the Emmy-nominated "Animal Rescue" television show. Hosted by animal lover Alex Paen, the program chronicles the rescue of a kitten trapped inside a wall, a cat stranded on top of a telephone pole and a kitty trapped inside of a burning building.
title: Animal Rescue: Vol. 2: Best Cat Rescues
